<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 03:14:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国驻菲律宾大使馆抗议日本大使就南海争议发表言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-embassy-philippines-protests-remarks-made-by-japan-ambassador-concerning-2024-08-29/</link><description>中国驻菲律宾大使馆周四表示，已向日本驻菲律宾大使馆发出外交照会，就中国大使就南海萨宾娜浅滩发表的“不负责任”言论表示抗议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 02:48:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-embassy-philippines-protests-remarks-made-by-japan-ambassador-concerning-2024-08-29/</guid></item><item><title>由于英伟达令人失望，亚洲股市跟随华尔街期货走低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-29/</link><description>周四，亚洲股市跟随华尔街期货走低，因英伟达的业绩令一些看涨投资者感到失望，而美元企稳，美国国债收益率曲线即将转正。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 02:30:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-29/</guid></item><item><title>在美国通胀测试之前美元保持上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-holds-gains-ahead-us-inflation-test-2024-08-29/</link><description>美元周四企稳，收复了前几个交易日的大幅跌幅，交易员期待本周末公布的关键美国通胀数据，该数据可能为利率前景提供进一步线索。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 01:18:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-holds-gains-ahead-us-inflation-test-2024-08-29/</guid></item><item><title>美国和中国官员将结束有关台湾和军事沟通的会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/us-chinese-officials-wrap-up-talks-beijing-taiwan-fentanyl-2024-08-29/</link><description>美国国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文周四会见了中国国家主席习近平的一位高级军事官员，他结束了在北京举行的为期三天的会谈，旨在缓解两个超级大国之间日益紧张的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 00:35:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/us-chinese-officials-wrap-up-talks-beijing-taiwan-fentanyl-2024-08-29/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院预计将对两名记者作出具有里程碑意义的煽动罪判决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-expected-hand-down-landmark-sedition-verdict-against-two-2024-08-29/</link><description>预计香港法院将于周四对一家现已解散的网络媒体的两名编辑作出判决，罪名是合谋发表煽动性文章，该案引起了国际社会的密切关注。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 00:26:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-expected-hand-down-landmark-sedition-verdict-against-two-2024-08-29/</guid></item><item><title>研究显示中国对非洲的贷款七年来首次增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-lending-africa-rises-first-time-seven-years-study-shows-2024-08-29/</link><description>周四的一项独立研究显示，中国银行去年向非洲批准了价值 46.1 亿美元的贷款，这是自 2016 年以来的首次年度增长。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 00:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-lending-africa-rises-first-time-seven-years-study-shows-2024-08-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：英伟达等待游戏结束，谨慎情绪下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-28/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 21:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：政府消息人士称，特斯拉要求加拿大降低对中国制造的电动汽车的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-asked-canada-lower-tariff-china-made-evs-government-source-says-2024-08-28/</link><description>加拿大政府消息人士周三表示，在加拿大本周表示将对中国制造的电动汽车征收 100% 关税之前，特斯拉已与渥太华接洽，要求降低其汽车的关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 21:17:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-asked-canada-lower-tariff-china-made-evs-government-source-says-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>郑在安德烈耶娃的惊吓中幸存，在美国公开赛上晋级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-survives-andreeva-scare-advance-us-open-2024-08-28/</link><description>周三，奥运冠军郑钦文在酷热的天气下以6-7(3) 6-1 6-2战胜俄罗斯选手埃里卡·安德烈耶娃，晋级美国公开赛第三轮。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 20:24:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-survives-andreeva-scare-advance-us-open-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>两名共和党人希望五角大楼将中国电池制造商宁德时代列入限制名单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/two-republicans-want-pentagon-add-chinese-battery-maker-catl-restricted-list-2024-08-28/</link><description>两名共和党高级议员周三要求美国国防部将中国电池制造商宁德时代列入涉嫌与北京军方合作的公司限制名单中。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 16:50:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/two-republicans-want-pentagon-add-chinese-battery-maker-catl-restricted-list-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟和中国启动促进工业数据流动的机制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/eu-china-launch-mechanism-facilitate-industrial-data-flows-2024-08-28/</link><description>欧盟周三在一份声明中表示，欧盟和中国在旨在简化跨境数据流动的新体系下启动了首次讨论。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 11:38:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/eu-china-launch-mechanism-facilitate-industrial-data-flows-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，制药商萌蒂的中国业务出售未能找到买家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/drugmaker-mundipharmas-china-unit-sale-fails-find-buyer-sources-say-2024-08-28/</link><description>两位知情人士称，亿万富翁萨克勒家族旗下的制药商萌蒂国际制药公司在今年的重新出售过程中第二次未能为其中国子公司找到买家。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 11:04:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/drugmaker-mundipharmas-china-unit-sale-fails-find-buyer-sources-say-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>香港开发商押注中国需求，转向租赁市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/betting-chinese-demand-hong-kong-developers-turn-rental-market-2024-08-28/</link><description>一些香港开发商现在转向住房租赁和租赁市场，以应对房地产市场的长期低迷，并满足中国内地专业人士和学生不断增长的租赁需求。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 08:05:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/betting-chinese-demand-hong-kong-developers-turn-rental-market-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>又有两家中国航空公司开始运营中国商飞C919客机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/two-more-chinese-airlines-start-flying-china-made-comac-c919-jet-2024-08-28/</link><description>据官方媒体中央电视台报道，国航和南航周三接收首架飞机后，将成为第二家和第三家运营中国商飞 C919 客机的中国航空公司。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 07:11:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/two-more-chinese-airlines-start-flying-china-made-comac-c919-jet-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>澳门法官宣布竞逐世界最大赌场中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/macau-judge-announces-bid-lead-worlds-biggest-casino-hub-2024-08-28/</link><description>澳门高级法官岑豪辉周三宣布，他打算在 10 月份竞选澳门行政长官，因为世界上最大的赌博中心正在努力将自己转变为主要的区域旅游目的地。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 03:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/macau-judge-announces-bid-lead-worlds-biggest-casino-hub-2024-08-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>